                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "ABSTRACT. In 2015, I. Soprunov and A. Zvavitch have shown how to use the Bernstein- Khovanskii- Kushnirenko theorem to derive non- negativity of a certain bilinear form "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
